.
Después warner brothers games  se decidió de darle la oportunidad a un pequeño estudio que tenia en ese momento poco mas de 35 empleados este studio  era ROCKSTEDY que decidió de darse la tarea de adaptar la historia de los cómics ARKHAM ASYLUM y contrataron a dos de las voces mas conocidas por sus personajes en la serie animada de BATMAN y esos son kevin konroy como BATMAN y mark hammil COMO EL JOKER, después de todo esto rockstedy finalizo el juego y lo lanzo al mercado siendo un gran éxito y después...

Have you been playing Link’s Awakening? I’ve been streaming it since last Friday and I absolutely love it! 💖It’s my first LoZ game ever~ ✨ The art style is totally adorable and I love the island setting. I reached the Animal Village on Monday and I was so delighted by how cute it is! 🐰 The dungeons are really cool, too—it’s been fun to learn about the different kinds of enemies you can encounter in the Zelda universe and what their strengths and weaknesses are. I’m really looking forward to streaming more tonight! 🌙 After I complete Link’s Awakening, which Zelda game should I try next? Let me know what your suggestions are in the comments ✨

caption.text:
Seven days of #kookievision, based on my latest Link's Awakening sugar cookie set. Day three. Roc's Feather. Made these using a faux-watercolour technique with @chefmaster food decorating pens. All you need is a little alcohol (I use vodka - it's flavourless and it evaporates completely) on your brush to blend the colours, and away you go.

If you want to see more, I created a 20 minute video compilation of the entire set. No instructions, no dialogue, just some music. Check out "Kookievision" on the Sweethart Baking Experiment YouTube channel to watch it.

For my favourite sugar cookie dough and royal icing recipe, visit the "How To" section of my website at sweethartbaking.com.

Do you love my cookie videos and want to see more? Check me out on Ko-Fi to make a small coffee-sized Paypal donation towards the future of Kookievision:
☕ ko-fi.com/sweethart

Music is "Floating Also" by William Rosati from the YouTube audio library.

#Nintendo #NintendoSwitch #NintendoSwitchLite #SuperMarioMaker2 #SmashBrosUltimate #SuperMario #SuperMarioOdyssey #CrashBandicoot #AnimalCrossing #ACNH #NewHorizons #Amiibo #Isabelle  #JoyCons #JustDance #Pokemon #PolemonLetsGo #Eevee

Ya podrás sentirte que estás conduciendo al estilo Mario Kart con dos volantes para el Nintendo Switch, el Mario Kart Racing Wheel, y el Mario Kart Racing Wheel DX.

Los volantes, cuales han sido desarrollado por Hori, también serán compatibles con PC, y contarán con las funciones de los Joy-Con y los Pro Controllers. Y para hacer la experiencia más completa, un pedal vendrá incluido en ambos modelos.

Aquellos que quieran reasignar los botones de los volantes, también podrán hacerlo, en adición a opciones de ajustes de zonas y realidad que permitirán alterar el giro del volante.

Sin embargo, los dispositivos solamente funcionarán cuando el Nintendo Switch esté conectado al televisor , pues requerirán de un accesorio adicional USB que presuntamente permitirá que se usen con el Switch Lite.

Por el momento, el Mario Kart Racing Wheel y su versión DX lanzarán en noviembre para Japón. El primero tendrá un costo de $64 dólares, y el segundo $130.

I know I sound entitled and spoiled but I miss my game room so much. When I tried getting my things I could only make it out with a few consoles and a few games before the police got there. The games dont even go to the consoles, but I'm thankful for what I did get. Those of you who had played games with me and took one step into my game room knew how passionate I was about taking care of them and the history they had. It breaks my heart to see almost all of it gone.
Videogames were such a big part of my life. The memories of finishing super mario 3d world with Jacob or playing Pokemon battles with trinity in German class will always be in my heart. They brought me close to those I loved 💚💜

Here are, what the #smashbroscommunity calls, the #creepiest #fighters in #smashbros, #thevillagers. I wanted their #casualoutfits to feel like #outfits you would see in #animalcrossing, I hope I achieved that aspect. I gave #malevillager a red shirt that says "Better Have My Bells" with the bag of money from Animal Crossing in reference to how you need to pay #tomnook with bells. For #femalevillager I gave her a cute #pinkflannel and you can't from this #drawing, but she's wearing a black shirt says "Shake them Trees" as not only a reference to how you get fruit in Animal Crossing, but also as a reference to a song by @blacknerd with the same name. I hope you guys like the #drawing.

Fortnite Season X Rocket Launch Event Sound Files Leaked:

Sound files from the upcoming Fortnite Season X rocket launch event have been leaked, and they include tapes left by and for the Visitor and fit overall into Fortnite's current storyline. Transcripts of said audio files were leaked last week, but now they have been revealed along with other sound files from the event itself.

Spoilers beware, but the audio files aren't as revealing as one might want. They include tapes, alarms from the rocket launch and sounds of an upcoming "NightNight" device which seems to be connected to the entire event.

There is also a countdown scheduled to appear above the rocket shortly, telling us when to expect it to launch. All this and more in the links below.

caption.text:
The latest issue of Dengeki PlayStation has new information on publisher Koei Tecmo and developer Gust’s upcoming Fairy Tail game.
.
Here are the information tidbits:
.
- The main story alone should be about 30 hours of gameplay.
- There is side content such as character episodes and special costumes, so it should actually take longer than 30 hours.
- Game-unique stories will appear, such as requests related to characters that do not appear much in the original manga or anime.
- There are more than 10 playable characters.
- There are costumes.
- Downloadable content is being considered.
- As your guild rank increases, your magic links will become greater and you can learn ultra magic-esque legend-class magic.
- By fulfilling the requests of the townspeople, you will be able to upgrade your guild’s various facilities.
- Your bonds with your party will deepen as you place them in your party or fulfill requests together.
- Battles are command-based, as previously announced. Play while considering things like, “when should I do this?,” “who should I do it to?,” “what magic should I use?,” and “who should I use it on?”
- Support character Makarov Dreyar can assist you with “Fairy Law”-esque ultra magic.
- There are characters that support each factility, job, and the lik within the guild.
.
Fairy Tail is due out for PlayStation 4, Switch, and PC worldwide in 2020.
.
#KoeiTecmo #Gust #FairyTail #anime #animation #manga #playstation #playstation4 #ps4 #switch #nintendoswitch #nintendo #pc #pcgaming #vg4n_FairyTail
.
Source: Gematsu

.

.

.
I love the axe though 😂 I'll be amazed if it makes it through the day in one piece! It's so fun to swing around ^^;
.
